      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• Both GETs fully public — no authMW\n  (main.go:168,216).\n• Page issues ZERO authenticated requests.\n• add-to-cart → in-memory cart only\n  (useCartStore.addItem, page.tsx:60-69).\n• POST /orders happens later on /menu.\n• Catalog mutations staff-only\n  (manager/admin) — not used here.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Both GETs fully public — no authMW\n  (main.go:168,216).\n• Page issues ZERO authenticated requests.\n• add-to-cart → in-memory cart only\n  (useCartStore.addItem, page.tsx:60-69).\n• POST /orders happens later on /menu.\n• Catalog mutations staff-only\n  (manager/admin) — not used here.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
