      "index": "z00022",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• productCacheTTL = 5 min\n  (product_service.go:21) — matches FE\n  staleTime 5 min → ~10 min worst case.\n• keys: combos:list · products:list.\n• write-triggered invalidation only —\n  none reachable from this page.\n• Redis fail-open: getCacheJSON swallows\n  errors → falls through to MySQL.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• productCacheTTL = 5 min\n  (product_service.go:21) — matches FE\n  staleTime 5 min → ~10 min worst case.\n• keys: combos:list · products:list.\n• write-triggered invalidation only —\n  none reachable from this page.\n• Redis fail-open: getCacheJSON swallows\n  errors → falls through to MySQL.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
