      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "z00026",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• No body/params bound → no 400 path.\n• Not-found is a CLIENT concept:\n  no GET /combos/:id, so missing combo =\n  rawCombos.find()→undefined →\n  \"Khong tim thay combo\" (page.tsx:86-93).\n• combos isError renders the SAME block.\n• products error → defaults [] (page.tsx:24)\n  → sub-items silently lose names/prices.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• No body/params bound → no 400 path.\n• Not-found is a CLIENT concept:\n  no GET /combos/:id, so missing combo =\n  rawCombos.find()→undefined →\n  \"Khong tim thay combo\" (page.tsx:86-93).\n• combos isError renders the SAME block.\n• products error → defaults [] (page.tsx:24)\n  → sub-items silently lose names/prices.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
