      "text": "combo row (combos table) +\n  combo_items rows joined →\n{ id, name, price=42000,\n  is_available:1,\n  combo_items:[{id,product_id,quantity}] }\n\nserializer emits ids only\n(product_handler.go:333-354) — names\nresolved client-side, never on the wire.",
